column5: I hit the Miss with the Missus on Friday  What a great day....  Here are some shots of the action  Crappie Time     Didn't keep any...  but probably should have.  We bagged a couple of other Green crappie... only two and they were released.  Had a nice pike follow but...  Tried a long walleye troll....nada
Some decent size crappie there!  thanks for sharing.
Must try and get up that way, thanks for the report...
Great report and pics Seaweed Real nice looking slabs Too bad about the eyes... I'm sure that it's just a matter of time before you get into some. Thanks for sharing Leechman
